recipesJson.name: mlNikon's strawnana Stacks
recipesJson.author: mixinvixens
recipesJson.description: pancakes with strawberries and banana slices on top. Inw strawberry shisha is a really nice syrupy strawberry and wf banana puree is a very authentic ripe banana. The wf Vanilla cream extra represents the ice cream on top of the pancakes. I left out the chocolate sauce because I did not want to muddle the mix.
